TopicTitle: Game crashing while flying in atmosphere

Articles.Content:
Hi @Konvict, likely you have this issue.

Please disable the highlighter in flight from the settings screen.

I was experiencing a similar issue.  During flight, KSP would crash whenever I held the right mouse button down to rotate the external camera IF my mouse's path intersected the ship model.  Highlighter off has fixed this so far.

 

(edit: only in 1.2.1)

Same problem, same scenario. Disabling and trying to reproduce.
